<p>I'm developing android app with G+ as SSO (Single sign on) functionality following this docs <a href="https://developers.google.com/identity/sign-in/android/sign-in" rel="nofollow">https://developers.google.com/identity/sign-in/android/sign-in</a></p>  <p>In my case, I need to create sign in and sign out in single button. When the user signed in I need to change the button text into "Sign Out". But </p>  <pre><code>SignInButton gPlusLoginButton = (SignInButton) findViewById(R.id.btGplus); // login implementation gPlusLoginButton.setText("Sign Out"); </code></pre>  <p>But SignInButton has no <code>.setText</code> method.</p>